# Dropbox app key for the web build (PKCE OAuth, no secret needed).
# Create a "Scoped access" app at https://www.dropbox.com/developers/apps with the
# permissions files.metadata.read, files.content.read, files.content.write, and add
# your site origin (e.g. http://localhost:1420/ and your deployed URL) to the app's
# OAuth 2 redirect URIs. Then copy the App key here.
VITE_DROPBOX_APP_KEY=
